{
  "stem": "5388.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were right square on the banks of the river Shchara.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the river going through Slonim.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to-- I heard somebody calling him, calling this Erren, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started to address him, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started my father was working for [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ausland, ?] and there was some other children that are also working, that our parents, their fathers, are working for outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And believe it or not, it's about eight or 10, me among them, and we went back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The others, they took away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They probably got killed, or they didn't send them to a sanitarium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- it must have been next month, in August.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Father must have made some arrangements to be able to run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what arrangement was-- I remember that [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lisa ?] came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was in a different camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was in this beutelager where Aaron was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember she came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And suddenly, we were out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And somebody met us with a, with a horse and buggy, a farmer, a Polish farmer, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he took us through the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Keep in mind that by that time, Grodno was part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Białystok was part of Germany, not occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and then we heard that it's in the German Reich the Jews are being treated better than what is in the occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we came by way of Volkovysk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we got to Grodno.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it was also quite-- we had to go through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's walking, and driving, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we came to Grodno in-- must have been September, October of 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Entered the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
